## Details

Servings: 4 with sufficient brown rice
Capicums: 2
Capsicum podi: 3 tsp
onion: 2 medium
garlic cloves: 2-3 medium


## Method
- Fry the onions and garlic in oil
- 2-3 tsp of capsicum powder
- keep aside

- fry chopped capsicum 
- wait till it softens

- grind all together with some water and salt as needed

